Authentication:

POST /api/auth/register/user: Register a new user.
POST /api/auth/register/vendor: Register a new vendor.
POST /api/auth/register/admin: Register a new admin.
POST /api/auth/verify-otp: Verify OTP.
POST /api/auth/login/user: Log in a user.
POST /api/auth/login/vendor: Log in a vendor.
POST /api/auth/login/admin: Log in an admin.


Admin:

GET /api/admin/users: Get all users.
PUT /api/admin/vendors/manage: Manage vendors.
GET /api/admin/analytics: View analytics.
DELETE /api/admin/users/:userId: Delete a user by ID.
DELETE /api/admin/vendors/:vendorId: Delete a vendor by ID.



Cart:

GET /api/cart: Get all items in cart.
POST /api/cart: Add an item to the cart.
DELETE /api/cart/:itemId: Remove an item from the cart by ID.
DELETE /api/cart: Clear all items from the cart.



Products:

GET /api/products: Get all products.
GET /api/products/:productId: Get a product by ID.
POST /api/products: Create a new product.
PUT /api/products/:productId: Update a product by ID.
DELETE /api/products/:productId: Delete a product by ID.



Sellers:

POST /api/sellers/register: Register as a seller.
GET /api/sellers/:sellerId: Get seller details by ID.
PUT /api/sellers/:sellerId: Update seller profile.
POST /api/sellers/add-product: Add product to seller's store.
POST /api/sellers/transaction: Handle wallet transactions.



Users:

GET /api/users/profile: Get user profile.
PUT /api/users/profile: Update user profile.
DELETE /api/users/profile: Delete user account.